window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They thought taking my Wrenny C was a good idea. </p> <p>They were wrong. </p> <p><i>Dead wrong</i>.<i> </i></p> <p>With Kingston and Sullivan by my side, we're on the hunt for those that threaten to rip our newfound family apart. But things are worse than we could have imagined. </p> <p>One thing's for sure: I'd give my life and my stash of ice cream to protect the ones I love. </p> <p><i>Fox on the Run</i> is the final book in the Crescent Valley Wolves duet. It is a paranormal shifter romance told in multiple POVs. The main character does not pick between the men. It contains mature scenes, male/male, and language.</p>"; 
